OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FBeggan spoke to Jennifer who waited
OL,8,Fdecades for a diagnosis
OL,10,FA woman who waited more than two
OL,11,Fdecades to be diagnosed with
OL,12,FEndometriosis is calling for more
OL,13,Fresearch into the condition.
OL,15,FJennifer Nuttall from Heywood, spent
OL,16,Fmore than double the usual time of
OL,17,Fnine years waiting for a diagnosis for
OL,18,Fthe often painful, chronic and
OL,19,Fdebilitating condition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
