PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FIt has no cure, but affects 1.5
OL,7,Fmillion women in the UK, with many
OL,8,Foften feeling like they are dismissed
OL,9,Fby medics.
OL,11,F"I first went to the doctor's when I
OL,12,Fwas 14, so that's 20 years ago now,
OL,13,Fand it was only in December 2025 that
OL,14,Fendometriosis was discussed," Jennifer
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"They said 'Has that not been
OL,18,Fmentioned to you?' And no, it hadn't.
OL,19,FI just thought I was weak."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
