OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FHer symptoms were severe. "It started
OL,7,Fwith debilitating period cramps, to
OL,8,Fthe point where it really impacted me
OL,9,Fat work," she said.
OL,11,FShe would have to pull over while
OL,12,Fdriving to be sick from the pain, she
OL,13,Fhad huge blood clots, exhaustion,
OL,14,Fbrain fog, and chronic acne.
OL,16,FDr Anita Sharma, an Endometriosis
OL,17,Fspecialist explained: "It's a
OL,18,Fcondition when the endometrial cells,
OL,19,Fwhich is the lining of the womb, grows
OL,20,Foutside the womb."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FShe said it causes severe debilitating
OL,7,Fpain which means women with the
OL,8,Fcondition often cannot get out of bed
OL,9,Ffor days at a time.
OL,11,F"It affects their mental, physical and
OL,12,Femotional wellbeing," Dr Sharma added.
OL,14,FThere is no cure for the condition
OL,15,Fcurrently. Jennifer said she's been
OL,16,Ftreated with "lots and lots of
OL,17,Fdifferent types of hormonal medication
OL,18,Fthat came with so many other
OL,19,Fsymptoms", but, "nothing's helped".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FShe was even given medication to
OL,7,Finduce menopause in her twenties,
OL,8,Fwhile it helped for a short time, when
OL,9,Fshe came off the medication she became
OL,10,Fmore unwell.
OL,12,FJennifer has a stepson, Jack, but she
OL,13,Fis desperate to have a child of her
OL,14,Fown.
OL,16,F"Knowing how endometriosis can affect
OL,17,Ffertility, I just, I can't wait any
OL,18,Flonger," she said.
OL,20,FWhat is Endometriosis?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
