OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FEndometriosis is a chronic condition
OL,7,Fwhere tissue similar to the lining of
OL,8,Fthe womb grows outside it, causing
OL,9,Fintense pelvic pain, fatigue and
OL,10,Ffertility issues.
OL,12,FSymptoms include:
OL,14,FMarch is endometriosis awareness
OL,15,Fmonth, drawing attention to the fact
OL,16,Fthere are one in ten women living with
OL,17,Fthe condition in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
