FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,FThose women will have been diagnosed
OL,7,Fthough the only test available on the
OL,8,FNHS, laparoscopic surgery, where
OL,9,Faffected lesions are removed from the
OL,10,Fabdomen.
OL,12,FPeter Gibson, co-founder of
OL,13,FEndometriosis Awareness North said:
OL,14,F"We need to support women with
OL,15,Fendometriosis and understand it a bit
OL,16,Fmore in the workplace... and be
OL,17,Fsupportive and encourage these women
OL,18,Fwho we call them warriors because it's
OL,19,Fa hell of a condition to have to deal
OL,20,Fwith.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
