PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774552271
OL,3,C'Nothing's helped': 20 years waiting
OL,4,Cfor endometriosis diagnosis
OL,6,F"If it was men that had it, it'd be
OL,7,Freally would be noisy about it."
OL,9,FJennifer wants women and doctors to
OL,10,Fwork together, so future generations
OL,11,Fdon't have to suffer like she does.
OL,13,F"As women we're in the same tax
OL,14,Fbrackets as men. Yet our care is
OL,15,Fsubstandard in comparison. The amount
OL,16,Fof money that's invested into
OL,17,Fresearch, it doesn't compare," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
